  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Date>

    public class Date
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Date>
    Date Class holds date that user account was created. Date class implements Comparable class and is used to compare two dates. Date class also has capability of validating a date.
